---

<BaseHead title="Master Azerbaijani - Home" />

<Header />

<main class="page-container">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Master Azerbaijani</h1>
    <p>Learn Azerbaijani from a diaspora native! Fun, bite-sized lessons for English speakers.</p>
    <p>
      Master it like a pro! Bridge generations in your family, embrace your heritage,
      and explore a language that opens doors; whether at home, with loved ones, or on your travels.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- LATEST POSTS -->
  <div class="latest-posts">
    <h2>Latest Posts</h2>
    <div class="post-grid">
      <div class="post-card"><a href="#">5 Fun Ways to Learn Azerbaijani</a></div>
      <div class="post-card"><a href="#">Why Learning Your Heritage Language Matters</a></div>
      <div class="post-card"><a href="#">Azerbaijani Alphabet Made Easy</a></div>
      <div class="post-card"><a href="#">Common Phrases for Everyday Use</a></div>
      <div class="post-card"><a href="#">Tips for Practicing Azerbaijani Daily</a></div>
      <div class="post-card"><a href="#">5 Common Phrases for Travelers</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WORD OF THE DAY -->
  <div class="word-of-day">
    <h2>Word of the Day</h2>
